  .form-group
    .form-check
      input#invalidCheck.form-check-input(type='checkbox' value='' required='')
      label.form-check-label(for='invalidCheck')
        | I Agree That All Informations are correct..
      .invalid-feedback
        | You must agree before submitting.
  button.btn.btn-primary(type='submit') Update 
  button#give.btn.btn-warning(type='button' onclick='history.go(-1)' ) Back


